@startuml
title Sequence - Search and Detail Flow
actor User
participant "Mobile App" as App
participant "API Server" as API
database "Postgres" as DB

User -> App : Nhập từ khóa
App -> API : GET /places?q=...
API -> DB : Query filtered places
DB --> API : rows
API --> App : total + items[]
User -> App : Chọn một place
App -> API : GET /places/:id
API -> DB : Query place detail + images + amenities + reviews
DB --> API : detail rows
API --> App : PlaceDetail JSON
App --> User : Render màn Detail
@enduml
